{
  "stem": "21437.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The, the, the end result was that they saved-- those girls, those remarkable girls-- they were heroines.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were heroes, really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And somehow, between them, each time somebody else-- when my name was called, somebody else answered for me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now I leave to your imagination what would happen if they would have been caught-- that they tried to defy because the German-- because this is what we were told.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You have to look at this body hanging there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because this is-- if you do anything out of place-- and he only escaped for a few-- he only stayed behind for a few hours.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So, you know, if they would have-- they would have realized how they did it, they probably-- they-- Whoever was going to answer for me stood behind.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because if there was a roll call, you didn't have your normal place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It wasn't a parade.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So you just ran out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Wherever-- you know, it was a certain spot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So wherever you stood that was in the middle of this, like, yard, surrounded by those dreary, drab places.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So in the middle, this is where it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So wherever you happened, they called, you ran out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And whatever-- you were once in the front, once in the back, once in the middle-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you really could not distinguish that much between those girls-- between the boys, too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You asked me this, Reuben.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know how-- because I told you this already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the interview?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said-- you ask me how they knew the girls and boys-- how could they say?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How they wouldn't know if there would be somebody else-- was it a girl or was it a boy?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You couldn't really-- their hair was so shortly cropped, you couldn't really necessarily know.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
